This product lattice defines a constraint for the AddSubtract actor such that inputs tagged as Random are also resolved to Unobserveable
This is a generic constraint that could apply to other actors. Creating a constraint for the AddSubtract actor only is sufficient for this example.

property.value: (output >= ObservableNonrandom && input >= UnobservableRandom) ? UnobservableRandom : (output >= ObservableNonrandom && input <= ObservableNonrandom) ? ObservableNonrandom : input
